101
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:07,010
[Apa kau bisa bangun?]

102
00:10:17,010 --> 00:10:21,290
[Gunung ini mendengarkan doa orang-orang.]

103
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:25,240
[Mungkin itu akan mendengar doaku]

104
00:10:25,870 --> 00:10:27,680
[yang ingin menyelamatkanmu.]

105
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:33,560
[Kematian lain di Gunung Jiri
telah dilaporkan.]

106
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:36,580
[Polisi menemukan tanda-tanda
pembunuhan dalam kasus ini]

107
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:40,360
[dan mereka sedang menyelidiki
tersangka utama.]

108
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,100
Kita harus bicara.

109
00:10:50,990 --> 00:10:53,590
Apa pun itu, kita bicara nanti.

110
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:01,280
Kita harus bicara sekarang.

111
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,000
Ini penting.

112
00:11:03,710 --> 00:11:07,280
Bukankah kau kabur ke kantor pusat
karena mengeluhkan kakimu?

113
00:11:07,370 --> 00:11:09,840
Apa kau datang bersama Yi-gang?

114
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,990
Kau juga mencurigai Komandan?

115
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:14,460
Tidak.

116
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,520
Bukan Komandan.

117
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:21,810
Kau bertanya kenapa aku kembali.

118
