area tempat korban ditemukan.

130
00:12:10,110 --> 00:12:15,070
[Lalu dia menemukan pita aneh
di dekat lembah di atas Air Terjun Gaeam.]

131
00:12:37,450 --> 00:12:38,630
[Pita?]

132
00:12:38,970 --> 00:12:40,690
Pita apa?

133
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:43,880
Seperti yang dipakai pendaki ilegal?

134
00:12:44,930 --> 00:12:46,110
Ya.

135
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:48,960
Bukan hanya di sana.

136
00:12:49,300 --> 00:12:50,220
[Nama korban: Choi Gi-yeong]

137
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:53,250
Kasus orang hilang ini terjadi
bulan Februari ini, di Lembah Oerae.

138
00:12:53,830 --> 00:12:56,940
Orang ini juga ditemukan
di dekat Batu Bongjaeam,

139
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,920
jauh dari tempat dia tersesat.

140
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:01,860
Komandan berpatroli
di area ini untuk berjaga-jaga

141
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:04,210
[dan menemukan satu set pita lagi.]

142
00:13:21,180 --> 00:13:23,280
[Di atas Air Terjun Gaeam
dan Batu Bongjaeam sangat berbahaya]

143
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,380
hingga pendaki ilegal
jarang pergi ke sana.

144
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:27,690
Namun kenapa ada pita di sana?

145
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,460
Seseorang menuntun mereka
ke sana untuk tersesat.

146
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:43,690
[Jalan di arah berlawanan dari puncak.]

147
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:46,040
[Penjahat membawa mereka
ke jalan pegunungan yang kasar]

148
00:13:46,160 --> 00:13:47,510
[di mana pendaki bisa mudah tersesat.]

149
00:13:48,850 --> 00:13:50,030
Namun

150
00:13:50,740 --> 00:13:52,210
bukan hanya pita.

151
