184
00:20:03,820 --> 00:20:05,250
Kau baik-baik saja?

185
00:20:11,170 --> 00:20:12,140
Yi-gang...

186
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:14,360
Mungkin karena salju lebat,

187
00:20:14,450 --> 00:20:16,090
tapi tidak ada sinyal radio.

188
00:20:16,170 --> 00:20:19,450
Aku akan memeriksa
apakah sinyal ponselku berfungsi.

189
00:20:20,450 --> 00:20:21,840
Tolong tunggu di sini sebentar.

190
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:33,430
Di atas es mengeras di jurang...

191
00:20:36,200 --> 00:20:38,220
Seseorang sengaja meninggalkan tongkat.

192
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:43,890
Hyun-jo, kau tahu...

193
00:20:49,060 --> 00:20:51,280
Bertahanlah.

194
00:20:52,290 --> 00:20:53,760
Aku akan segera kembali.

195
00:21:10,310 --> 00:21:12,700
[Dia keluar untuk melapor]

196
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:16,190
dan tidak pernah kembali.

197
00:21:18,330 --> 00:21:21,940
Benar, kudengar
dia menghubungi pos pagi itu.

198
00:21:45,080 --> 00:21:47,180
Pos Jagawana Haedong.

199
00:21:49,280 --> 00:21:50,670
[Jembatan Hitam...]

200
00:21:51,010 --> 00:21:52,310
[Yi-gang terluka.]

201
00:21:53,950 --> 00:21:55,500
Halo? Hyun-jo?

202
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:58,360
Aku tidak bisa mendengarmu. Di mana kau?

203
00:21:58,440 --> 00:21:59,950
[Lembah Jembatan Hitam!]

204
00:22:01,930 --> 00:22:03,690
